Entity Note

Action perform_note_creation
  EventInput
    space_id    required
    body        required
    title       optional
    note_date   optional
  BusinessRules
    - space_id must reference an Active Space owned by the actor
  Steps
    - Create Note record with type = manual, status = Active
    - If note_date not provided: set to today
  SideEffects
    - None  (manual notes do not generate automatic notes)
  ActionResult
    note_id   UUID

Action perform_note_update
  EventInput
    note_id             required
    title, body, note_date  optional
  BusinessRules
    - At least one field must be provided
  Steps
    - Update provided fields on Note record
  SideEffects
    - Trigger create_automatic_note with type = note_edited
      referencing this note_id
  ActionResult
    note_id         UUID
    updated_fields  string[]

Action perform_note_archive
  EventInput
    note_id   required
  Steps
    - Update Note status to Archived
  SideEffects
    - None
  ActionResult
    note_id   UUID

Action notify_already_archived
  Steps
    - No state change
  Outcome
    NoAction    NOTE_ALREADY_ARCHIVED

Action reject_request
  Steps
    - No state change
  Outcome
    NoAction    REQUEST_REJECTED

Action perform_automatic_note_creation
  EventInput
    space_id, type, body, note_date   required
    reference_id, reference_type      optional
  BusinessRules
    - type must not be "manual" — automatic notes are never of type manual
    - space_id must reference an existing Space (Active or Archived)
      Note: automatic notes are written even if space is Archived
      to preserve the audit trail
  Steps
    - Create Note record with provided type, status = Active
  SideEffects
    - None  (automatic notes do not trigger further automatic notes)
  ActionResult
    note_id   UUID
